lead_paragraph: Leaders Barcelona's Anoeta Stadium jinx struck again when they lost 1-0 at Real Sociedad on Saturday, their second successive defeat in La Liga.

headline.print_headline: Barca Lose Again at Sociedad, Record for Ronaldo
